{
  "title": "Fried Kenyan Okra Stir-fry",
  "description": "A tender and fermented okra dish that is a crowd-pleaser in Kenya, featuring sunflower oil for a unique twist on the traditional recipe.",
  "cuisine": "Kenyan",
